<!-- Purpose: Test the HSPACE attribute with the IMG element. (i.e.img src="eggplant.gif" hspace=15) -->

<!-- Expected result: There are two images below. The HSPACE value for the images is 20 and 50, respectively. The distance between the text and the image should increase from image 1 to image 2. -->

<title>XHTML Functional -- IMG - HSPACE</title>

</head>

<body>

<img src="images/eggplant.gif" alt="Kiss me, I'm an eggplant!"

hspace="20" /> HSPACE adds white space on both the left and right

side of the image. The graphic to the left of this paragraph has

HSPACE set to 20 pixels. <br clear="left" />

 <img src="images/eggplant.gif" alt="Kiss me, I'm an eggplant!"

hspace="50" /> HSPACE adds white space on both the left and right

side of the image. The graphic to the left of this paragraph has

HSPACE set to 50 pixels.

</body>

